{"tid":864793,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"自卑=自大","createTime":"2018-10-16T12:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T14:59:18.000Z","uid":142657,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"36c7bf73fe73fb5fc8274088879cd659f5bd5a19","tid":864793,"uid":142657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:50:11.000Z","msg":"其實我意思係<br />\n過分自卑嘅人覺得自己冇野叻<br />\n人人都俾佢好<br />\n自己係世界上最差最渣最慘嘅一個<br />\n<br />\n但其實你係邊過姐？<br />\n大把人慘過你<br />\n憑乜嘢覺得自己比其他人慘<br />\n自己吾選擇同人人一樣解決問題<br />\n反而仲係到埋怨<br />\n要幾咁自我中心，幾咁自大嘅人先會咁諗<br />\n<br />\n所以吾洗同情啲自卑嘅人<br />\n佢哋只係吾去面對問題嘅人，仲用籍口去博同情，想全世界就佢一個<br />\n<br />\n吾係自大，係咩？"},{"pid":"57b90cf15b58959997f40a16a9526ec92efcb4d2","tid":864793,"uid":191815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T14:19:52.000Z","msg":"吾你老母咩 你就真撚係自大嗱"},{"pid":"a84e3bd745bcf3b47040c5cf975bd28a59a389b7","tid":864793,"uid":116105,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:03:56.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;大把人慘過你&rdquo; 這句很公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3842f26b94e6e99752c90c1abbfdf6e7926b104","tid":864793,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:13:35.000Z","msg":"自卑就覺得全世界欠咗佢，然後就要人地應該對佢好，咁就係自大。"},{"pid":"ef7df7dfb19d80fa28284bf050776165d6c3516a","tid":864793,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a84e3bd745bcf3b47040c5cf975bd28a59a389b7","tid":864793,"uid":116105,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:03:56.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;大把人慘過你&rdquo; 這句很公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:16:31.000Z","msg":"玩撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa62c97e406b00abcb412dcb4b14738679d7760","tid":864793,"uid":206416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:59:18.000Z","msg":"此post 完結。88"}]}